# GIF

Kind: global class

# giF.fetch(type) ⇒ Promise.<string>

Returns a random GIF image of the type provided.

Kind: instance method of GIF
Returns: Promise.<string> - The Formatted GIF URL.

Param Type Description
type string The Type of GIF. See https://weebyapi.xyz/api/docs#gif for all the GIFs.
